## ğŸ§ª API Endpoints (Sample)

| Method | Endpoint            | Description   |
| ------ | ------------------- | ------------- |
| POST   | /api/token/         | Login         |
| POST   | /api/token/refresh/ | Refresh token |
| GET    | /api/tasks/         | List tasks    |
| POST   | /api/tasks/         | Create task   |

